name: Blue Floral Patterned Pocket
description:
Each pocket is hand-made, therefore each pattern will vary,  making each pocket unique. 

Pocket will be shipped with iron-on adhesive and instructions to secure onto t-shirt of your choice.

*Pockets are for aesthetic purposes and may not be used for full functionally.

*Purchase does not include t-shirt. Pictures are solely to visualize pocket on a t-shirt.
